{
  "name": "markdown-ai-translate-by-junes",
  "displayName": "Markdown AI Translate By junes",
  "description": "使用 OpenAI 兼容接口翻译 Markdown 文件，打开临时双栏预览，并尽量保留标题、列表、表格、引用、链接和代码块等 Markdown 格式。",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "publisher": "junes",
  "license": "MIT",
  "icon": "resources/icon.png",
  "keywords": [
    "translate",
    "markdown",
    "translation",
    "bilingual",
    "chinese",
    "openai",
    "deepseek",
    "llm"
  ],
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.85.0"
  },
  "categories": [
    "Other"
  ],
  "activationEvents": [
    "onLanguage:markdown",
    "onCommand:markdownAiTranslate.translate",
    "onCommand:markdownAiTranslate.openSettings",
    "onCommand:markdownAiTranslate.clearCache"
  ],
  "main": "./dist/extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "markdownAiTranslate.translate",
        "title": "翻译 Markdown（双栏预览）",
        "category": "Markdown AI Translate By junes",
        "icon": "resources/icon.svg"
      },
      {
        "command": "markdownAiTranslate.openSettings",
        "title": "打开 Markdown AI Translate 设置",
        "category": "Markdown AI Translate By junes"
      },
      {
        "command": "markdownAiTranslate.clearCache",
        "title": "清除 Markdown 翻译缓存",
        "category": "Markdown AI Translate By junes"
      }
    ],
    "menus": {
      "editor/title": [
        {
          "command": "markdownAiTranslate.translate",
          "when": "resourceLangId == markdown",
          "group": "navigation"
        }
      ]
    },
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Markdown AI Translate By junes",
      "markdownDescription": "需要清除翻译缓存时，请在命令面板运行 **清除 Markdown 翻译缓存**。",
      "properties": {
        "markdownAiTranslate.apiEndpoint": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "https://api.openai.com/v1",
          "order": 1,
          "markdownDescription": "OpenAI 兼容 API 地址，例如 `https://api.deepseek.com/v1`。"
        },
        "markdownAiTranslate.apiKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "order": 2,
          "markdownDescription": "翻译服务 API Key。"
        },
        "markdownAiTranslate.model": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "gpt-4o-mini",
          "order": 3,
          "markdownDescription": "模型名称，例如 `gpt-4o-mini`、`deepseek-chat`。"
        },
        "markdownAiTranslate.targetLanguage": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "中文",
          "order": 4,
          "markdownDescription": "目标翻译语言，例如中文、日文、韩文。"
        },
        "markdownAiTranslate.customPrompt": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "你是一名专业翻译。请把用户提供的文本翻译成目标语言。\n规则：\n- 保留所有 Markdown 格式，包括标题、列表、链接、图片、行内代码等\n- 不要修改任何占位符，例如 __URL0__、__CODE0__、__SEGMENT_0_START__ 或 __SEGMENT_0_END__\n- 不要翻译 URL 或图片路径\n- 保持原有段落结构\n- 只输出翻译后的文本，不要输出任何解释",
          "order": 5,
          "editPresentation": "multilineText",
          "markdownDescription": "自定义系统提示词。默认填充内置 Markdown 翻译提示词；如果清空该设置，插件仍会使用内置提示词。修改时请保留对 Markdown 格式和 `__URL0__`、`__CODE0__`、`__SEGMENT_0_START__` 等占位符的保护要求。"
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "scripts": {
    "compile": "esbuild src/extension.ts --bundle --outfile=dist/extension.js --external:vscode --format=cjs --platform=node --target=node18",
    "watch": "esbuild src/extension.ts --bundle --outfile=dist/extension.js --external:vscode --format=cjs --platform=node --target=node18 --watch --sourcemap",
    "lint": "tsc --noEmit",
    "package": "npx @vscode/vsce package --out \"release/Markdown AI Translate By junes-1.0.0.vsix\""
  },
  "devDependencies": {
    "@types/markdown-it": "^14.1.2",
    "@types/node": "^20.0.0",
    "@types/vscode": "^1.85.0",
    "esbuild": "^0.20.0",
    "typescript": "^5.4.0"
  },
  "dependencies": {
    "markdown-it": "^14.0.0"
  }
}
